Product description

Enrich your look with this Sling Bag from KLEIO available on Amazon. KLEIO offers handbags in every style, shape and color. It’s a perfect accessory for your outfits. Match it with pair of heels/sandals to give complete look.

From the manufacturer

Kleio Slingbag For Girls/Women




Sling Bag for Women

Kleio presents this sling bag for women which is made from PU and canvas material and is available in a shade of black and brown with pretty polka dots design on its exterior.

It comes with a PU strap which makes it easy to carry and makes it an ideal choice while choosing a sling bag.

Sleek and Attractive Bag

The sling bag has a magnetic button and a drawstring closure type. It has one compartment along with one pocket for your accessory.

With a product dimension of 25.4 cm x 7.6 cm x 30.4 cm, it is compact and easy to carry.

For College and Outings

The sling bag is a good choice for picnics and outings when you want to carry your essential stuff in an organized manner.

It can also be used as a backpack that adds a style statement to your personality. You can match this bag with your casual or semi-casual outfit of your choice to complete the look.

How does Amazon calculate star ratings?
Amazon calculates a product's star ratings based on a machine learned model instead of a raw data average. The model takes into account factors including the age of a rating, whether the ratings are from verified purchasers and factors that establish reviewer trustworthiness.
